Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:30.82,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}人生在世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:37.41,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}究竟为了追寻什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:42.55,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}睡过头的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:49.21,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}也日复一日地清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:23:01.71,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:07.90,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}因为这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:14.56,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}总是需要你的存在
